data.description: Why wait for new construction? When you can buy this almost new home with added upgrades. $15,000 for closing cost. This beautiful 4 bedrooms / 2 bathrooms home located in the Murano at Westside community. Built in 2019, this home is a must see! Tile floors throughout the home with upgraded waterproof laminate flooring in 3 bedrooms. Upon entering you have two spacious room on your right with a full bathroom. Further down the hall to your left is your third bedroom next to a laundry room. Spacious kitchen with lots of cabinet space, large island and a large walk in pantry! Kitchen opens up into the dining and living area, including updated light fixture in dining room and over sized ceiling fan in the living room. The master suite features a beautiful bathroom with a spacious walk in shower and a granite countertop with double sinks, large linen closet and a walk in closet. Backyard patio opens up into a spacious backyard with screen in the lanai and with privacy fenced off on all sides with gate located on the side of the home. This community offers resort style pool and a community playground. Located in close proximity to Disney parks, Disney Springs, Margaritaville, Golf, Entertainment, Dining, Shopping and more! Quick access to all major highways.
